{"tid":663631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"囡囡唱廣東兒歌 梁詠琪冧到流眼淚","createTime":"2018-05-13T12:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T12:53:51.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d4310b7e89719e29bb306f06ecc676fb6c7791","tid":663631,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）老公Sergio代理的西班牙童裝品牌，位於尖沙咀限定店今日正式開幕，GiGi兩公婆現身外，囡囡Sofia卻未有出現。GiGi原來擔心人流多，不敢帶囡囡同行，而母親節會跟自己的媽媽和婆婆飲茶，四代同堂慶祝。提到囡囡的第一份母親節手工禮物，GiGi說：「原來她講錯，不是Macaron（馬卡龍），是Macaroni（通心粉），她用通心粉造了一條手鍊給我，又在學校學了一首廣東兒歌唱給我聽，家裡好少跟她講中文，她唱『我愛我的媽媽、媽媽真偉大，媽媽教我努力，做個好乖乖。』，當下感動到我流下一滴眼淚。」GiGi指可能囡囡看過演唱會後，壯膽好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180513/s00007/78a33528f6037a8453d7ebcc9af150b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180513%2Fs00007%2F78a33528f6037a8453d7ebcc9af150b2.jpg&h=c5a1aea0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02dcd1ed6872d6a08814ccd5724c9a8a3f78c3ca","tid":663631,"uid":10427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span>"},{"pid":"9eac8c3451b5c4aed55a9a8ff9b336dca6e420ad","tid":663631,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"02dcd1ed6872d6a08814ccd5724c9a8a3f78c3ca","tid":663631,"uid":10427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae5beb4994919139a895dcafa62c060b9d1328b1","tid":663631,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以收嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}